<h2>Klen 3.0</h2>
<p class="sub">April 2026</p>
<p class="intro"><strong>Plink is now Klen</strong> &mdash; <em>[kl&#603;n]</em>. Inspired by Scandinavian precision, Klen is the leanest way to capture tasks in the heat of the moment. This release marks the transition from prototype to a fully standalone app with its own identity.</p>
<h3>New</h3>
<ul>
<li><span class="tag new">New</span> <strong>New name &amp; identity</strong> &mdash; Plink is now Klen. Every string, menu item, and system reference updated.</li>
<li><span class="tag new">New</span> <strong>New app icon</strong> &mdash; Clean, modern, unmistakably Klen.</li>
<li><span class="tag new">New</span> <strong>About section</strong> &mdash; Name, pronunciation [kl&#603;n], slogan and version in Settings &rarr; Advanced.</li>
<li><span class="tag new">New</span> <strong>Reset Onboarding</strong> &mdash; Revisit the intro anytime from Settings &rarr; Advanced.</li>
</ul>
<h3>Improved</h3>
<ul>
<li><span class="tag imp">Improved</span> App icon shown in Onboarding welcome screen</li>
<li><span class="tag imp">Improved</span> Bundle ID updated to <code>com.simonlang.Klen</code></li>
<li><span class="tag imp">Improved</span> Backups now use <code>.klenbackup</code> format</li>
<li><span class="tag imp">Improved</span> All strings updated in English and German</li>
</ul>
<h3>Bug Fixes</h3>
<ul>
<li><span class="tag fix">Fix</span> Completed tasks found via search now always visible regardless of 30-min window</li>
<li><span class="tag fix">Fix</span> Monthly recurrence from Jan 31 no longer produces unexpected date</li>
<li><span class="tag fix">Fix</span> Soft-deleted tasks without deletion timestamp no longer risk premature purge</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<p class="slogan">Noted in a blink. Organized in Klen.</p>
</body></html>
